launcher.title: Uirlisí
launcher.description: Liosta uirlisí. Is taispeántas úsáideach é seo.

infohub_tools_checksum.YOU_CAN_GENERATE_A_CHECKSUM_FROM_THE_DAT: Is féidir leat a ghiniúint checkum ó na sonraí a théann tú isteach.
infohub_tools_checksum.YOU_CAN_SELECT_WHAT_NODE_WILL_GENERATE_T: Is féidir leat a roghnú cad a bheidh nód ghiniúint an checkum.
infohub_tools_checksum.YOU_CAN_SELECT_WHAT_TYPE_OF_CHECKSUM_YOU: Is féidir leat a roghnú cén cineál checkum mian leat.
infohub_tools_checksum.IS_USED_IN_SWEDEN_AS_A_PERSONAL_IDENTIFI: Tá sé in úsáid i sweden mar aitheantóir pearsanta nó aitheantóir cuideachta.
infohub_tools_checksum.YOU_CAN_ENTER_A_PERSONNUMMER_IN_THIS_FOR: Is féidir leat duine a chur isteach san fhormáid seo:
infohub_tools_checksum.YY_=_TWO_DIGIT_YEAR,_MM_=_TWO_DIGIT_MONT: Yy = dhá bhliain dhigit, mm = dhá mhí dhigit, dd = dhá lá dhigit na míosa,
infohub_tools_checksum.THE_CHECKSUM_WILL_CALCULATE_THE_FOURTH_(: Beidh an checkum ríomh ar an ceathrú (last) dhigit.
infohub_tools_checksum.SELECT_WHAT_CHECKSUM_METHOD_YOU_WANT_TO_: Roghnaigh cad é an modh is mian leat a úsáid
infohub_tools_checksum.WHAT_NODE_PLUGIN_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_PRODUCE_: Cén breiseán nód ar mhaith leat a thabhairt ar aird ar an checkum?
infohub_tools_checksum.WHAT_TYPE_OF_CHECKSUM_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_CRE: Cén cineál checkum is mian leat a chruthú?
infohub_tools_checksum.YOUR_DATA_YOU_WANT_A_CHECKSUM_FOR_KEY: Do shonraí is mian leat checkum do
infohub_tools_checksum.WILL_SHOW_THE_CHECKSUM_KEY: An mbeidh a thaispeáint ar an checkum

infohub_tools_compress.YOU_CAN_WRITE_YOUR_TEXT_IN_THE_TEXT_BOX_: Is féidir leat scríobh do théacs sa bhosca téacs: compress na sonraí.
infohub_tools_compress.YOU_CAN_SELECT_WHAT_NODE_AND_METHOD_YOU_: Is féidir leat a roghnú cad a nód agus modh mian leat a úsáid chun compress na sonraí.
infohub_tools_compress.CLICK_THE_BUTTON:_COMPRESS._CLICK_ON:_DE: Cliceáil ar an gcnaipe: comhbhrúite. Cliceáil ar: decompress, a fheiceáil ar an toradh.
infohub_tools_compress.REMOVE_THE_TEXT_YOU_WROTE._NOW_CLICK_THE: Bain an téacs a scríobh tú. Anois cliceáil ar an gcnaipe: decompress.
infohub_tools_compress.WHAT_NODE_SHOULD_COMPRESS_YOUR_DATA?_KEY: Cad ba chóir nód comhbhrúite do shonraí?
infohub_tools_compress.WHAT_COMPRESSION_METHOD_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_U: Cén modh comhbhrú ar mhaith leat é a úsáid?
infohub_tools_compress.WILL_SHOW_THE_RESULT_KEY: An mbeidh a thaispeáint ar an toradh
infohub_tools_compress.WHAT_NODE_SHOULD_DECOMPRESS_YOUR_DATA?_K: Cad ba chóir nod decompress do shonraí?
infohub_tools_compress.WHAT_DECOMPRESSION_METHOD_DO_YOU_WANT_TO: Cén modh dí-chomhbhrúite a theastaíonn uait a úsáid?

infohub_tools_encrypt.THIS_TOOL_CAN_ENCRYPT_AND_DECRYPT_YOUR_T: Is féidir an uirlis criptithe agus decrypt do téacs
infohub_tools_encrypt.SELECT_WHAT_ENCRYPT_METHOD_YOU_WANT_TO_U: Roghnaigh cad modh criptithe mian leat a úsáid
infohub_tools_encrypt.WHAT_NODE_PLUGIN_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_ENCRYPT\: Cén breiseán nód mian leat a chriptiú / a dhíchriptiú ar?
infohub_tools_encrypt.WHAT_TYPE_OF_ENCRYPTION_METHOD_DO_YOU_WA: Cén cineál modh criptithe ar mhaith leat a úsáid?

infohub_tools_package.VIEW_DATA_FROM_MESSAGES_ENCODED_KEY: Féach ar shonraí ó theachtaireachtaí ionchódaithe
infohub_tools_package.WITH_THIS_TOOL_YOU_CAN_VIEW_DATA_FROM_TH: Leis an uirlis is féidir leat féachaint ar shonraí ó na teachtaireachtaí maoine pacáiste ionchódaithe.
infohub_tools_package.SEE_YOUR_BROWSER_NETWORK_TAB_IN_DEVELOPE: Féach ar do tab líonra bhrabhsálaí in uirlisí forbróir.
infohub_tools_package.WILL_SHOW_THE_DECODED_PRETTY_JSON_KEY: An mbeidh a thaispeáint ar an json decoded deas

infohub_tools_password.PASSWORD_LENGTH_=_LENGTH_OF_THE_PASSWORD: Fad Pasfhocal = fad na pasfhocail mian leat.
infohub_tools_password.MAX_GROUP_NUMBER_=_NUMBERS_OF_GROUPS_TO_: Uasuimhir ghrúpa = líon na ngrúpaí a chur san áireamh sa focal faire.
infohub_tools_password.DEFAULT_MAX_GROUP_NUMBER_=_4_(0-4)_SOME_: Default max uimhir ghrúpa = 4 (0-4) nach bhfuil roinnt suímh a cheadú spásanna, ansin a leagtar max uimhir ghrúpa = 3.
infohub_tools_password.SOME_SITES_DO_NOT_ALLOW_SPECIAL_CHARACTE: Ní roinnt láithreáin a cheadú carachtair speisialta, ansin a leagtar uimhir ghrúpa max = 2.
infohub_tools_password.SELECT_WHAT_PASSWORD_FORMAT_YOU_WANT_TO_: Roghnaigh cad formáid phasfhocal is mian leat a úsáid
infohub_tools_password.WHAT_NODE_PLUGIN_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_PRODUCE_: Cén breiseán nód ar mhaith leat a thabhairt ar aird ar an checkum?
infohub_tools_password.WHAT_GROUPS_DO_YOU_WANT_IN_YOUR_PASSWORD: Cad iad na grúpaí ar mhaith leat i do phasfhocal?
infohub_tools_password.WHAT_PASSWORD_LENGTH_DO_YOU_WANT?_KEY: Cén fad focal faire ar mhaith leat?
infohub_tools_password.WILL_SHOW_THE_PASSWORDS_KEY: An mbeidh a thaispeáint ar an focal faire

infohub_tools_random.WITH_THIS_TOOL_YOU_CAN_GET_THE_CURRENT_R: Leis an uirlis is féidir leat a fháil ar an randamach reatha i bhformáidí éagsúla
infohub_tools_random.SELECT_WHAT_RANDOM_FORMAT_YOU_WANT_TO_US: Roghnaigh cad formáid randamach mian leat a úsáid
infohub_tools_random.WHAT_NODE_PLUGIN_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_PRODUCE_: Cén breiseán nód ar mhaith leat a thabhairt ar aird ar an checkum?
infohub_tools_random.WILL_SHOW_THE_RANDOM_NUMBER_KEY: An mbeidh a thaispeáint ar an uimhir randamach

infohub_tools_testcall.WITH_THIS_TOOL_YOU_CAN_WRITE_TEST_CALLS_: Leis an uirlis is féidir leat glaonna tástála a scríobh agus feidhmeanna a spreagadh.
infohub_tools_testcall.PRACTICAL_IF_YOU_WANT_TO_DEBUG_A_SPECIFI: Praiticiúil más mian leat feidhm ar leith a dhiúltú.
infohub_tools_testcall.WRITE_YOUR_TEST_CALL_AND_SEND_IT_KEY: Scríobh do ghlaoch tástála agus é a sheoladh
infohub_tools_testcall.SELECT_A_TEMPLATE_FOR_THE_CALL_YOU_WANT_: Roghnaigh teimpléad don ghlaoch is mian leat
infohub_tools_testcall.THE_CALL_YOU_WANT_TO_MAKE_KEY: An glao is mian leat a dhéanamh

infohub_tools_time.WITH_THIS_TOOL_YOU_CAN_GET_THE_CURRENT_T: Leis an uirlis is féidir leat a fháil ar an am reatha i bhformáidí éagsúla
infohub_tools_time.OBSERVE_THAT_THE_SERVER_PHP_PLUGIN_MUST_: Breathnaigh go gcaithfidh an breiseán php freastalaí a fhios faoi do chrios ama.
infohub_tools_time.SEE_THE_DOCUMENTATION_FOR_INFOHUB_TIME_H: Féach ar an doiciméadacht le haghaidh am infohub conas a athrú go
infohub_tools_time.SELECT_WHAT_TIME_FORMAT_YOU_WANT_TO_USE_: Roghnaigh cén fhormáid ama is mian leat a úsáid
infohub_tools_time.WHAT_NODE_PLUGIN_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_PRODUCE_: Cén breiseán nód ar mhaith leat a thabhairt ar aird ar an checkum?
infohub_tools_time.WHAT_TIME_FORMAT_DO_YOU_WANT?_KEY: Cén fhormáid ama ar mhaith leat?
infohub_tools_time.WILL_SHOW_THE_TIME_IN_THE_RIGHT_FORMAT_K: An mbeidh a thaispeáint ar an am i bhformáid ceart

infohub_tools_uuid.YOU_CAN_GENERATE_A_UUID4_FROM_THE_CLIENT: Is féidir leat a ghiniúint uuid4 as an breiseán cliant nó as an mbreiseán freastalaí
infohub_tools_uuid.YOU_CAN_GET_A_UUID4_KEY: Is féidir leat a fháil uuid4
infohub_tools_uuid.WHAT_NODE_PLUGIN_DO_YOU_WANT_TO_PRODUCE_: Cén breiseán nód ar mhaith leat a tháirgeadh ar an uuids?
infohub_tools_uuid.WHAT_VERSION_(FLAVOUR)_OF_THE_UUID_DO_YO: Cén leagan (blastán) den uuid is mian leat?
infohub_tools_uuid.WILL_SHOW_THE_UUID_KEY: An mbeidh a thaispeáint ar an uuid
